### Optimization Recommendations System

The system will analyze household appliances, energy consumption, battery capacity, and household needs to generate personalized recommendations that help extend available backup power during an outage.

#### 1. Appliance Priority Recommendations

The system will suggest priority levels for each appliance based on:

* Importance during a power outage
* Energy consumption
* Medical or accessibility requirements

Users may modify these priorities at any time.

#### 2. Optimization Usage Instructions

The system will provide actionable recommendations to reduce unnecessary energy consumption, including:

* Turning off non-essential devices
* Unplugging unused electronics
* Reducing active lighting
* Limiting high-energy appliances
* Prioritizing critical household loads

#### 3. Runtime Improvement Analysis

The system will compare the current appliance configuration with an optimized configuration and display:

* Current estimated runtime
* Optimized estimated runtime
* Total runtime gained from applying recommendations

This allows users to understand how energy-saving actions can extend backup power during outages.
